WHATS_THE_DATE_OF_BIRTH: What is the date of birth? For example, 1st of January, 1990.
WHATS_THE_YEAR_OF_BIRTH: What is the year of birth? For example, 1990.
WHATS_THE_TIME_OF_BIRTH: What is the time of birth? For example, 9 PM. If you are unsure, you can say I don't know.
WHATS_THE_PLACE_OF_BIRTH: What's the city, or country of birth? For example, Paris. If you are unsure, you can say I don't know.
NATAL_CHART_OF_PERSON_BORN_ON: Here is the natal chart of the person born on %s
PLANET_SIGN_OF_PERSON_BORN_ON: The %s sign of a person born on %s is %s
MISSING_OBJECTS: Planets that are not mentioned require time or place of birth. Those include %s Ascendant, Midheaven and the other houses.
MISSING_INFO: Apologies, I checked again for you, but I really need to know %s of birth. Try to get this information and come back to me.
DATE_RANGE_ERROR: Sorry, I can only check for year of birth between 1550 and 2649. Let's try again. Tell me the year of birth.
